Here is my intellij color theme.  It is a work in progress, but I have been tuning this over the period of 2 years.
.
.
To use the color scheme, go to File > Import Settings > Find the .jar > Choose Color Scheme and click next.  Enjoy.
.
.
.
Here are some vm args to make things run smoother -XX:MaxPermSize=150m -XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC -XX:+CMSIncrementalMode -XX:+CMSIncrementalPacing -XX:+AggressiveOpt -XX:+UseBiasedLocking -XX:+CMSPermGenSweepingEnabled -XX:+CMSClassUnloadingEnabled -XX:+DoEscapeAnalysis
  

This file was modified by IntelliJ IDEA 10.5.2 for binding GitHub repository